{"tid":96633,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人一出世就要背負責任","createTime":"2017-01-27T04:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T03:35:00.000Z","uid":79353,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3640b9e0bc365c80710df08dbbc8fd72b53eae84","tid":96633,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"呢個係大部分人出世之後所行的人生路。<br />\n<br />\n細個係讀小學中學<br />\n爭入band1中學<br />\n讀好d書<br />\n為考好dse 入大學神科 賺錢科。<br />\n<br />\n讀好書之後就要出黎做野賺錢<br />\n仲要俾家用供養父母。<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔怕俾人鄙視<br />\n屋企又對你的無所事事冇乜意見<br />\n你可以試下唔返學又唔做野。<br />\n<br />\n不過大部分人都要煩前途<br />\n呢d野喺社會眼中係人與生俱來就要負的責任。<br />\n<br />\n一定要跟呢條路行<br />\n否則你就不是一個別人眼中合格的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743644dbf690a0a52d0b7ae4cbdd4f330aeef1ca","tid":96633,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"雖然我係咁講者<br />\n不過我曾經都有為所謂前途努力過<br />\n而結果係衰左。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634b5ca336b9855d126a429ee6d301ec4b0a8caa","tid":96633,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"屋企個個月頭都追收家用<br />\n雖然唔係話要我好多<br />\n不過我太廢人工好低<br />\n俾左家用之後都所剩無幾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773bfe67e6141ed0624e02ca7aa8f3cf2d0b0ccd","tid":96633,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"你到底係為左自己負責任定為左其他人<br />\n介意人點睇既係你 將來既日子都係你自己要負責"},{"pid":"fba9f23b5af1181cb48a9f68ac7b358de3591a87","tid":96633,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你到底係為左自己負責任定為左其他人<br />\n介意人點睇既係你 將來既日子都係你自己要負責</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95089e72fe67c03d9e868793e13d4a1220d7343","tid":96633,"uid":36756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04