e.vjmedia.com.hk%2F2016%2F03%2F08%2F15056&d=avmIg8rHyY0amRrLLBcajWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8872aeee\" target=\"_blank\">http://style.vjmedia.com.hk/2016/03/08/15056</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都search 到<br />\n仲睇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我意思係你覺得篇文邊度有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152e843cfa046241bd32834f3370cd35f7a6b3ce","tid":96633,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"再簡單講, 你負責任, 是因為要生存. 甚至為達到目標或者提高生活質素, 所以要負更大責任<br />\n<br />\n可能你覺得好殘酷, 但現實就係咁<br />\n在非洲草原上, d野豬跑慢d都比獅子食左, 佢地都唔係為左生存咩? 當然又客觀講, 如果隻野豬可以唔負責任, 比獅子食左就算, 佢唔洗搵食物, 唔洗辛苦的跑"},{"pid":"93b3e691b6f061ffa8157422e8f0233450146cb0","tid":96633,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"安樂死?<br />\n唔洗返工阿?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed8a491dd9932db394ba511b9599ffb8d60c433","tid":96633,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:15:40.000Z","msg":"父母當年養大自己既恩情<br />\n本身回饋返比自己仔女其實就足夠（養大佢地）<br />\n奈何香港福利唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n退左休仲要上街汁紙皮，所以父母希望養兒防老<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2db799ff5a3f4d65fe19277a6e4c63b02a017e","tid":96633,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e11da5d2f6ff7356b1ec6335139070bc437099f","tid":96633,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhi"},{"pid":"9978eaf5c59977e5ac711ff95c085fc0ba5d656e","tid":96633,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安樂死?<